        "name": "Ancestral Winds",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You call on the same energies that manifest ancestor storms, summoning wailing spirits to terrorize your foes. Living creatures in the area take 5d6 void damage and 1d6 mental damage and must attempt a Will save. Nonliving creatures are immune to this spell\u2019s effect.",
